name: Schedule
title: Schedule
description: A container for slots of time that may be available for booking appointments.

elements.name: Schedule
elements.description: A container for slots of time that may be available for booking appointments.

elements.name: active
elements.description: Whether this schedule record is in active use or should not be used (such as was entered in error).

elements.name: serviceCategory
elements.description: A broad categorization of the service that is to be performed during this appointment.

elements.name: serviceType
elements.description: The specific service that is to be performed during this appointment.

elements.name: specialty
elements.description: The specialty of a practitioner that would be required to perform the service requested in this appointment.

elements.name: actor
elements.description: Slots that reference this schedule resource provide the availability details to these referenced resource(s).

elements.name: planningHorizon
elements.description: The period of time that the slots that reference this Schedule resource cover (even if none exist).

elements.name: comment
elements.description: Comments on the availability to describe any extended information.
